#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.33 LTS, our new LTS version."
msgstr "Hemos lanzado Quarkus 3.33 LTS, nuestra nueva versión LTS."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is our pleasure to announce the release of Quarkus 3.33, which is our new LTS (Long Term Support) version."
msgstr "Tenemos el placer de anunciar el lanzamiento de Quarkus 3.33, que es nuestra nueva versión LTS (Long Term Support)."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This version is built on the top of Quarkus 3.32.\n"
"New features landed in https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-34-released/[Quarkus 3.34], which was also released today."
msgstr "Esta versión está construida sobre Quarkus 3.32. Las nuevas características aterrizaron en link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-34-released/[Quarkus 3.] 34, que también fue lanzado hoy."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you want to know more about our LTS policy, the https://quarkus.io/blog/lts-releases/[LTS announcement] is a must read."
msgstr "Si quiere saber más sobre nuestra política link:https://quarkus.io/blog/lts-releases/[de L] TS, el link:https://quarkus.io/blog/lts-releases/[anuncio de LTS] es una lectura obligada."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "LTS releases are supported for 12 months."
msgstr "Las versiones LTS reciben soporte durante 12 meses."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
