#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Note that `quarkus update` should handle most of the heavy lifting for you,\n"
"but there are still cases that should be handled manually and we recommend reading these migration guides carefully."
